desc = <<EOD
Keekar's Parental Control Package for pfSense

A comprehensive parental control package that helps parents manage and limit 
their children's internet access time.

Features:
- Profile-based device grouping with shared time accounting
- Daily and weekly time limits with weekend bonus
- Flexible scheduling (bedtime, school hours, custom periods)
- Service-specific monitoring (YouTube, Facebook, TikTok, etc.)
- Bot detection to prevent phantom usage
- DHCP/ARP auto-discovery of devices
- Real-time status dashboard with usage tracking
- RESTful API for external integrations
- OpenTelemetry-compliant JSONL logging
- Bypass-proof enforcement (MAC + IP tracking)

This package provides enterprise-grade parental controls with advanced features
like per-service time limits, intelligent bot detection, and comprehensive logging.
EOD
