message = <<EOM
====================================================================
Keekar's Parental Control v1.4.67 has been installed successfully!
====================================================================

To configure the service:
1. Go to Services > Parental Control in pfSense web interface
2. Enable Parental Control service
3. Create child profiles and add devices
4. Configure time limits and schedules
5. Set up service-specific monitoring (optional)

The package includes:
- Automatic cron job for usage tracking (runs every 5 minutes)
- Real-time monitoring dashboard at Status > Parental Control
- Health check endpoint at /parental_control_health.php
- RESTful API at /parental_control_api.php
- JSONL logs at /var/log/parental_control.jsonl

Documentation: https://github.com/keekar2022/KACI-Parental_Control

